{"tid":1751342,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"熱狗準備去收支票，拉倒一個泛民一千萬","createTime":"2019-11-24T17:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T17:01:58.000Z","uid":335157,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c70d6fdf845999cd685c548659efbce7334b1e64","tid":1751342,"uid":335157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:01:58.000Z","msg":"我今日發咗個白日發<br />\n<br />\n夢裡我是一名熱狗，兼任連登分化師<br />\n<br />\n收到一張現check 有一千萬<br />\n<br />\n發達了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 周圍同人講投建制 <br />\n你估無油水？派咗咁多mon post狗，分化撚<br />\n<br />\n老人家果啲海馬牌，白米濕濕碎<br />\n<br />\n等柒婆同全世界講 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">香港市民支持止暴制亂<br />\n全香港人同暴力割蓆 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">寧投建制 不投泛民</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n泛民雖然城府深，做事陰濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係都會係前線屌狗，幫手拖延<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄺神同許智峯嘅表現大家有目共睹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無佢哋努力宣傳<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">逃犯條例</span></span><br />\n<br />\n港豬都唔會醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傻囝比我呃曬<br />\n<br />\n然後，夢醒了 我去咗投票"}]}